## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Luxturna 2017** = first FDA gene therapy USA. AAV2 RPE65 voretigene neparvovec — Leber congenital amaurosis (RPE65). 양안 subretinal injection $850K. cross-sensory + iag. quantum-VQE 의 AAV capsid + receptor 가 entry point.
2. **Zolgensma 2019** = first FDA AAV CNS gene therapy. AAV9 SMN1 onasemnogene abeparvovec — SMA Type 1 IV infusion. $2.1M 1회 dose. AAV9 BBB cross. cross-iag + pediatric_rare.
3. **Hemgenix + Roctavian 2022-2023** = AAV5 F9 + F8 hemophilia. $3.5M Hemgenix (highest-ever drug price 2023). Roctavian liver toxicity LFT 일과성 + immunosuppression prophylaxis.
4. **Casgevy + Lyfgenia 2023** = first FDA ex-vivo CRISPR (Casgevy exa-cel) + lentivirus β-globin (Lyfgenia lovo-cel) sickle cell 동시 승인. CRISPR clinical 적용 paradigm shift. cross-hem2.
5. **NTLA-2001 in-vivo CRISPR ATTR 2021-22** = first-in-human in-vivo CRISPR (LNP delivery, hepatic). Phase 3 MAGNITUDE 진행. wet-lab clinical 의미.
6. **VERVE-101 base editing PCSK9 2022** = first-in-human base editing — heterozygous FH. ABE-LNP heart attack 1회 dose lifetime LDL-C 감소.
7. **patisiran + vutrisiran + inclisiran + nusinersen 2016-2022** = LNP-siRNA + GalNAc-siRNA + ASO IT — modality-platform 변천. patisiran first LNP-siRNA → vutrisiran GalNAc Q3M switch (TTR modality 변천 모범 사례). inclisiran Q6M → 환자 compliance.
8. **AAV pre-existing nAb 10-30%** = AAV5 + AAV9 자연 항체 prevalence — 성인 환자 배제 + 한국 식약처 framework 부재. capsid evolution + capsid switch (AAV5 → Anc80 → DELIVER) 가 next-gen escape strategy.
9. **LMO2 leukemia 1999-2008** = γ-retrovirus SCID-X1 임상 4/9 환자 T-ALL 발생. enhancer insertion mutagenesis lessons → SIN (self-inactivating) lentivirus + insulator + 4HSC4hot-spot integration site profile. 현재 lentivirus 안전성 향상.
10. **bluebird bio EU 철수 2022** = Zynteglo + Skysona EU pricing 협상 결렬. commercial 어려움. 1회 dose lifetime cure $1.5-3.5M paradigm — payer 가 multi-year amortization 거부. quantum-only in-silico, gene therapy 임상 의미 한정.

